sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Admin
    participant CurriculumDashboard as Curriculum Dashboard
    participant CurriculumController as Curriculum Controller
    participant Database

    Note over Admin, Database: UC-07: Manage Topics (Curriculum Structure)

    Admin->>CurriculumDashboard: Selects "Create New Topic"
    CurriculumDashboard-->>Admin: Display input fields (Name, Description, Parent Module)
    Admin->>CurriculumDashboard: Enters details & clicks "Save"
    CurriculumDashboard->>CurriculumController: createTopic(name, description, parentId)
    CurriculumController->>Database: checkTopicNameUniqueness(name, parentId)
    Database-->>CurriculumController: isUnique

    alt Duplicate Topic Name
        CurriculumController-->>CurriculumDashboard: Error: "A topic with this name already exists"
        CurriculumDashboard-->>Admin: Block creation & show error
    else Input Valid / Unique
        CurriculumController->>Database: create_topic(name, description)
        Database-->>CurriculumController: return new topicId
        Note right of CurriculumController: Step 7: Enable immediate adaptive practice
        par Initialize Student Mastery
            CurriculumController->>Database: fetchAllStudentIds()
            Database-->>CurriculumController: list of students
            CurriculumController->>Database: bulkInsertTopicMastery(topicId, stability=0, difficulty=5.0)
        end
        CurriculumController-->>CurriculumDashboard: Topic created successfully
        CurriculumDashboard-->>Admin: Show confirmation: "Ready to add questions"
    end

    Note over Admin, Database: Management Flow (Edit or Delete)

    alt Admin chooses to Edit
        Admin->>CurriculumDashboard: Selects existing topic
        CurriculumDashboard->>CurriculumController: getTopicDetails(id)
        CurriculumController->>Database: fetchTopicData(id)
        Database-->>CurriculumController: topic_details
        CurriculumController-->>CurriculumDashboard: Display edit form
        Admin->>CurriculumDashboard: Updates fields & clicks "Save"
        CurriculumDashboard->>CurriculumController: updateTopic(id, data)
        CurriculumController->>Database: update_details(name, description)
        Database-->>CurriculumController: success
        CurriculumController-->>CurriculumDashboard: update confirmed
    else Admin chooses to Delete
        Admin->>CurriculumDashboard: Clicks "Delete"
        CurriculumDashboard-->>Admin: Warning: "Cascade delete will remove questions/mastery"
        Admin->>CurriculumDashboard: Confirm "Delete Forever"
        CurriculumDashboard->>CurriculumController: performCascadeDelete(id)
        par Delete Linked Entities
            CurriculumController->>Database: deleteLinkedQuestions(id)
            CurriculumController->>Database: deleteTopicMastery(id)
            CurriculumController->>Database: deleteTopic(id)
        end
        Database-->>CurriculumController: success
        CurriculumController-->>CurriculumDashboard: removal confirmed
        CurriculumDashboard-->>Admin: Refresh curriculum view
    end